@startuml
!theme plain

title Real-time Stock Market Prediction System - Control Flow

actor "CSV Data Source" as CSV
participant "producer.js" as Producer
participant "Kafka Topic\n(Stock Data)" as KafkaTopic
participant "consumer.js" as Consumer
participant "ml_consumer.js" as MLConsumer
participant "pre_process.js\n(MinMaxScalar)" as Preprocessor
participant "MongoDB" as DB
participant "server.js\n(HTTP/Socket.IO)" as Server
participant "tf_train.js" as Trainer
participant "tf_model.js\n(LSTM Model)" as Model
participant "tf_validate.js" as Validator
participant "Client" as Client

== Data Ingestion Phase ==
CSV -> Producer: Read stock data from CSV
activate Producer
Producer -> KafkaTopic: Publish stock data
activate KafkaTopic
deactivate Producer

== Data Storage Phase ==
KafkaTopic -> Consumer: Consume stock data
activate Consumer
Consumer -> DB: Store stock data logs
activate DB
deactivate Consumer
deactivate DB

== Model Training Phase ==
Client -> Server: Request model training
activate Server
Server -> Trainer: Trigger training
activate Trainer
Trainer -> DB: Retrieve historical stock data
activate DB
DB --> Trainer: Return training dataset
deactivate DB
Trainer -> Preprocessor: Scale training data
activate Preprocessor
Preprocessor --> Trainer: Return scaled data
deactivate Preprocessor
Trainer -> Model: Define LSTM architecture
activate Model
Model --> Trainer: Return model instance
Trainer -> Model: Train model with data
Model --> Trainer: Return trained model
Trainer -> Model: Save model weights
Model -> Model: Persist weights to disk
Model --> Trainer: Weights saved
deactivate Model
Trainer --> Server: Training complete
deactivate Trainer
Server --> Client: Training status
deactivate Server

== Model Validation Phase ==
Client -> Server: Request model validation
activate Server
Server -> Validator: Trigger validation
activate Validator
Validator -> DB: Retrieve test dataset
activate DB
DB --> Validator: Return test data
deactivate DB
Validator -> Preprocessor: Scale test data
activate Preprocessor
Preprocessor --> Validator: Return scaled test data
deactivate Preprocessor
Validator -> Model: Load model weights
activate Model
Model --> Validator: Model loaded
Validator -> Model: Generate predictions on test data
Model --> Validator: Return predictions
deactivate Model
Validator -> Validator: Calculate performance metrics
Validator -> DB: Store performance metrics
activate DB
deactivate DB
Validator --> Server: Validation complete
deactivate Validator
Server --> Client: Validation results
deactivate Server

== Real-time Prediction Phase ==
KafkaTopic -> MLConsumer: Consume real-time stock data
activate MLConsumer
MLConsumer -> Preprocessor: Preprocess incoming data
activate Preprocessor
Preprocessor --> MLConsumer: Return scaled data
deactivate Preprocessor
MLConsumer -> Model: Load pre-trained model
activate Model
Model --> MLConsumer: Model ready
MLConsumer -> Model: Generate real-time predictions
Model --> MLConsumer: Return predictions
deactivate Model
MLConsumer -> MLConsumer: Log predictions
MLConsumer -> DB: Store predictions (optional)
activate DB
deactivate DB
deactivate MLConsumer
deactivate KafkaTopic

@enduml
